      "text": "早上要刷牙，晚上也要刷牙。上刷刷，下刷刷，左刷刷，右刷刷。",
      "translation": "Brush teeth in the morning, brush teeth at night. Brush up, brush down, brush left, brush right."
    },
    {
      "text": "刷完牙齿白白的，嘴巴香香的。没有蛀牙，身体棒棒的！",
      "translation": "After brushing, teeth are white and mouth is fresh. No cavities, healthy body!"
    }
